---
import PageHeader from "@/components/PageHeader";
import SiteFooter from "@/components/SiteFooter.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — studio.list"
  description="How studio.list selects, documents, and presents independent design agencies."
>
  <PageHeader active="about" client:load />
  <main class="about-page">
    <h1 class="sr-only">About studio.list</h1>
    <div class="about-content">
      <section>
        <h2>What is studio.list?</h2>
        <p>
          studio.list is an independent directory for discovering design
          agencies through the work and identity they publish themselves. It is
          built for useful browsing—not rankings, ads, or paid placement.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>Why we built it</h2>
        <p>
          Finding the right studio usually means moving between scattered lists,
          search results, and recommendations. studio.list puts the official
          website first, so you can compare agencies through their own work and
          move directly to the source.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>What belongs in the index?</h2>
        <p>
          An agency is published only when its official website is reachable and
          an unobstructed, authentic homepage screenshot can be captured. Entries
          are deduplicated by official domain and ordered consistently by name.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>How is it maintained?</h2>
        <p>
          Descriptions and locations are preserved from the source data.
          Screenshots show the desktop homepage above the fold at 1440 × 900 and
          can be refreshed when a site changes or an update is requested.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>Independence</h2>
        <p>
          studio.list is not affiliated with the agencies shown. Names, logos,
          descriptions, and website imagery remain the property of their
          respective owners. Every profile links directly to the official site.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>
